data.description: Welcome to an extraordinary gem in Plantation Bay! This waterfront pool home offers luxury, comfort, and smart living. Step inside to an open floor plan where the living, dining, and family rooms seamlessly blend. Vaulted ceilings and ample windows bathe the home in natural light. Upgrades include the remodeled Chef's kitchen which boasts 39-inch soft-close cabinets, granite countertops, and top-of-the-line appliances. Industrial grade, energy efficient ductless split total home HVAC system. Entire home  water filtration and softener, 80-gallon hybrid water heater. This home even has remote controlled and programmable blinds! All big ticket items were done in 2020 (HVAC, Roof, Water heater, pool and lanai. Move in and enjoy the remarkable features of this practical and beautiful home!
